ValidationForm is a Form
    Layout
        display as text
            visible when (ValidationFailed)
                header3 of "<ConfigSnapshotItemInfo.Name>ValidationStatus"
                single column
                    ConfigValidationStatus.Status
                        no label
                        display as tag
                            color of red
                    ConfigValidationStatus.ValidationErrorText
                        no label
                    ErrorText
            visible when (ConfigBundleSnapshot.ConfigValidationStatus.Status.Failed)
                header3 of "OverallSnapshotValidationStatus"
                single column
                    ConfigBundleSnapshot.ConfigValidationStatus.Status
                        no label
                        display as tag
                            color of red
                    ConfigBundleSnapshot.ConfigValidationStatus.ValidationErrorText
